ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This is a Node.js + Express + MongoDB backend application developed as part of the BucketStudy Full Stack Development Internship.

The backend provides secure REST APIs for:

User Authentication (Register & Login)

Employee Management (CRUD operations)

JWT-based Authorization

All APIs were tested using Thunder Client.

