ğŸ” Authentication APIs
1ï¸âƒ£ Register User

POST /api/auth/register

Request Body

{
  "name": "Admin",
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "role": "admin"
}


ğŸ“¸ Screenshot: 01_register_user.png

2ï¸âƒ£ Login User

