â–¶ï¸ How to Run the Backend
Step 1: Install Dependencies
npm install

Step 2: Create .env File
PORT=5000
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key

Step 3: Start Server
npm run dev


Server will run at:

http://localhost:5000

